These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, country, rock, soul
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, azalea, aconite
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, indonesian, colombian, polish
1. the italian is the fan of soul##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4
4. the indonesian is on the left or right of the polish##3
5. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
6. the polish is on the left of the fan of rock##1
7. the indonesian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the polish is between the person who growsaconite and the fan of classical##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | soul      | classical | country | rock |
| Flower   | azalea | daisy  | begonia   | aconite    |
| Nationality     | italian     | colombian    | polish    | indonesian      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea, soy-milk, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, climbing, rugby, ice-hockey
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, pop, funk, gospel
1. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
2. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
4. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is between the person drinking water and the person drinking iced-tea##2
8. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person drinking soy-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage         | water | soy-milk   | iced-tea | tea  |
| Sport   | rugby     | golf | ice-hockey  | climbing |
| Music-Genre     | gospel        | funk  | pop    | dubstep |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, photographer, doctor, teacher
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, sunflower, poppy
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, camping, baking, sudoku
1. the person who growspoppy is between the librarian and the teacher##2
2. the person who growsrose is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is the doctor##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the teacher##1
5. the teacher is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growssunflower is between the photographer and the person who growsiris##2
7. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job          | librarian | photographer   | teacher     | doctor     |
| Flower   | rose  | poppy | sunflower   | iris  |
| Hobby     | sudoku      | camping | baking | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, reading, traveling, sudoku
City: edinburgh, rome, prague, nizza
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, tram, boat, subway
1. the person traveling to nizza is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
5. the person traveling to nizza is the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
7. the person traveling to prague is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks  | sudoku   | traveling     | reading |
| City   | prague  | nizza      | edinburgh        | rome     |
| Transport         | boat | snowmobile | subway | tram   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, hamster, guinea-pig, frog
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, project-manager, bartender, mechanic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, aristoff, chaman, ritmeester
1. the owner of the frog is the mechanic##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
3. the tiparillo-smoker is the mechanic##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the mechanic##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the project-manager is on the far left##1
7. the owner of the hamster is on the far right##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
9. the writer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Pet   | goat   | frog   | guinea-pig | hamster |
| Job         | project-manager      | mechanic | writer      | bartender |
| Cigar     | aristoff | tiparillo        | ritmeester       | chaman  |

