.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, havana, oliveros, fonseca
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, hot-chocolate, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, black, ivory, yellow
1. the havana-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is the havana-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who likes black##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
7. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar    | oliveros   | fonseca      | havana       | aristoff |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | sprite | hot-chocolate     | juice |
| Color     | yellow     | black  | blood-red | ivory |

