.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, havana, bluemaster, tiparillo
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, snooker, go
City: berlin, miami, boston, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to boston is the person playing bridge##1
2. the person traveling to miami is between the person playing go and the person traveling to berlin##2
3. the person playing go is the havana-smoker##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
5. the dunhill-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person playing go is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
7. the person playing bridge is the dunhill-smoker##1
8. the person traveling to boston is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Cigar      | bluemaster   | tiparillo          | havana | dunhill        |
| Game   | snooker     | domino | go   | bridge     |
| City           | berlin | miami         | san-francisco         | boston |

