.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, orange, lavender, turquise
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, march, january, september
There 4 different types of food: apricot, artichoke, zucchini, grapefruit
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
3. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
4. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Color   | orange         | ivory  | lavender     | turquise         |
| Birthday        | september | march | june | january         |
| Food      | artichoke         | zucchini  | apricot   | grapefruit |

