.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
House: cape-cod, townhouse, wooden, modern
4 different games are played: domino, go, chess, whist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, weightlifting, handball, cycling
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
 2. the person playing domino is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 4. the person playing chess is between the townhouse house and the cape-cod house##2
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is the wooden house##1
 7. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
 8. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
 9. the person playing go is between the modern house and the wooden house##2
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| House   | cape-cod  | wooden    | townhouse | modern    |
| Game   | domino | chess | go  | whist |
| Sport           | handball   | cycling    | basketball        | weightlifting   |

