.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, snake, cat, lizard
House: farmhouse, townhouse, cottage, ranch-style
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, lilac, azure, ivory
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the cottage house##3
4. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
5. the owner of the cat is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
6. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the townhouse house##1
7. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the townhouse house##1
8. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet      | chinchilla                | lizard  | snake | cat   |
| House           | ranch-style | townhouse | farmhouse   | cottage |
| Color   | lilac         | blood-red     | ivory     | azure |

