3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the victorian house##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the wooden house and the person who's hobby is camping##2
6. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Flower          | poppy    | daisy  | rose  | daffodil |
| House   | wooden | victorian | gothic-revival | ranch-style |
| Hobby   | fishing    | board-games     | camping    | magic-tricks |

