.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, ship, taxi, boat
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, electrician, analyst, lawyer
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, collecting, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person driving the taxi and the engineer##2
2. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
3. the analyst is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the electrician##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
6. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
7. the engineer is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
8. the analyst is the person driving the roller##1
9. the lawyer is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Transport      | roller | taxi      | ship  | boat    |
| Job   | analyst   | electrician | lawyer | engineer |
| Hobby           | woodworking      | collecting       | magic-tricks   | chess      |

