.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, march, october
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, dancer, videographer, dressmaker
There 4 different types of food: spinach, apricot, apple, zucchini
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person eating spinach##2
3. the person eating apricot is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
5. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating apple##1
6. the dressmaker is between the person eating spinach and the librarian##2
7. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
8. the dancer is in an even position##4
9. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | november    | march | july  | october  |
| Job   | videographer | dancer       | dressmaker | librarian |
| Food         | apple   | spinach      | zucchini | apricot       |

