.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, pall-mall, dunhill, alhambra
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, chef, scientist, writer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, aconite, daisy
1. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
2. the person who growszinnia is the pall-mall-smoker##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the chef##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is the writer##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the lawyer is the person who growszinnia##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the alhambra-smoker##1
8. the person who growsdaisy is the alhambra-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Cigar      | dunhill      | pall-mall | tiparillo     | alhambra    |
| Job   | writer | lawyer      | chef | scientist |
| Flower           | aconite   | zinnia  | balloon-flower     | daisy |

