.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, egyptian, chinese, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, metal, reggae, soul
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, marigold, azalea
1. the canadian is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
2. the fan of rock is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
4. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
5. the egyptian is between the person who growssunflower and the fan of reggae##2
6. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan of soul##1
7. the egyptian is on the left of the canadian##1
8. the fan of rock is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Nationality    | chinese    | egyptian     | canadian    | indonesian        |
| Music-Genre       | reggae   | rock | metal | soul |
| Flower   | azalea | marigold      | sunflower    | amaryllis   |

