.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, august, october
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, train, helicopter, snowmobile
4 different pets are kept: mouse, snake, pony, hedgehog
1. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the snake and the person who's birthday is in october##2
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in october is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Birthday          | february | october  | may   | august    |
| Transport   | skateboard  | helicopter     | snowmobile | train |
| Pet   | pony   | hedgehog | mouse | snake   |

