City: colone, rome, marseilles, prague
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, techno, r&b, indie
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is the person traveling to rome##1
5. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
6. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the fan of techno is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Sport         | rugby | badminton   | skiing    | volleyball    |
| City           | prague   | rome    | colone | marseilles |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | jazz | r&b    | indie         |

