1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who likes ebony is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Color   | yellow | grey | ebony | mauve   |
| Birthday   | february    | december   | april     | september    |
| Sport   | soccer  | badminton | weightlifting  | volleyball |

