.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, photographer, engineer, videographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, indie, ambient, jazz
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, milk, iced-tea
1. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
4. the engineer is on the far left##1
5. the photographer is between the fan of jazz and the fan of techno##2
6. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the firefighter##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Job    | engineer    | photographer    | firefighter  | videographer |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | indie | techno | ambient      |
| Beverage     | coffee   | cola        | iced-tea   | milk       |

 